snippet.title: Trick Shot - Out Now
snippet.description:
A game where all you have to do is throw a ball into a box, simple? Trick Shot is a minimalist physics puzzler with 90 levels and an infinite supply of bouncy balls to get that perfect shot. Find it on the App Store here https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/trick-shot/id1016915419?ls=1&mt=8

Music by Graham Hadfield
http://grahamhadfield.com/
